*[[IPA]]: /pɒli'hiːdrən/ (''plural'' /pɒli'hiːdrə/)
*[[SAMPA]]: /<tt>pQli"hi:dr@n</tt>/ (''plural'' /<tt>pQli"hi:dr@</tt>/)

===Noun===
{{en-noun2|'''polyhedron'''|'''[[polyhedra]] '''or''' [[polyhedrons]]'''}}

#{{geometry}} A [[solid]] [[figure]] with many [[face]]s.
#{{optics}} A [[polyscope]], or multiplying glass.

